5000|$|Private property: The <b>means</b> <b>of</b> <b>production</b> are {{no longer}} {{in the hands of the}} monarchy and its nobles, but rather they are {{controlled}} by the capitalists. The capitalists control the <b>means</b> <b>of</b> <b>production</b> through commercial enterprises (such as corporations), which aim to maximise profit.|$|R
